  "content": "\n \n \n  <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_content__xNUGz\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack w-full flex-wrap gap-4\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\"><br></p></div></div>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr article_coverImage__8wj6a\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"900\" height=\"471\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image_intrinsic__ulrJk image_lightMode__SmqSs\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/73N0dZEENNBHEK030NFGlR/3828c3c9fb2c2a55937fea47c838b372/MCP.jpg, https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/73N0dZEENNBHEK030NFGlR/3828c3c9fb2c2a55937fea47c838b372/MCP.jpg\" src=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/73N0dZEENNBHEK030NFGlR/3828c3c9fb2c2a55937fea47c838b372/MCP.jpg\">\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/introduction\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">MCP (Model Context Protocol)</a> is a way to build integrations for AI models.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Vercel now supports deploying MCP servers (which AI models can connect to) as well as MCP clients (<a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI chatbot</a> applications which call the servers).</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/templates/next.js/model-context-protocol-mcp-with-next-js\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Get started with our server template</a> or continue reading to learn more.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#how-is-mcp-different-than-apis?\" id=\"how-is-mcp-different-than-apis?\">How is MCP different than APIs? \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">APIs allow different services to communicate together. MCP is slightly different.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Rather than thinking about MCP like a REST API, you can instead think about it like a tailored toolkit that helps an AI achieve a particular task. There may be multiple APIs and other business logic used behind the scenes for a single MCP tool.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">If you are already familiar with <a href=\"https://ai-sdk.dev/docs/ai-sdk-core/tools-and-tool-calling\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">tool-calling in AI</a>, MCP is a way to invoke tools hosted on a different server.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">MCP now supports a protocol similar to other web APIs, namely using HTTP and OAuth. This is an improvement from the previous stateful <a href=\"https://v0.dev/chat/QokL3arwn1E\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Server-Sent Events (SSE)</a> protocol.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#deploying-mcp-servers-to-vercel\" id=\"deploying-mcp-servers-to-vercel\">Deploying MCP servers to Vercel \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">To simplify building MCP servers on Vercel, we’ve published a new package <code>@vercel/mcp-adapter</code> which supports both the older SSE transport and the newer stateless HTTP transport.</p>\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-code-block_wrapper__G_cQP\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block_wrapper__t6FCO code-block_hasFileName__ezlBD blog-code-block_codeBlock__s7CJU\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <div class=\"code-block_header__t3NRd\">\n      <div class=\"code-block_fileName__HmSv1\">\n       <span class=\"code-block_filenameP__02nok\">app/api/[transport]/route.ts</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"code-block_actions__yphRf\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block_copyButton__uo5Yu\" type=\"button\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-javascript code-block_pre___OLfy blog-code-block_maxHeight__pAjn3\"><code class=\"code-block_code__isn_V\"><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword module\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token imports\"> createMcpHandler </span><span class=\"token imports punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'@vercel/mcp-adapter'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> handler </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">createMcpHandler</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">server</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token arrow operator\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  server</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">tool</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token string\">'roll_dice'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token string\">'Rolls an N-sided die'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sides</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> z</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">min</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token parameter\"> sides </span><span class=\"token parameter punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token arrow operator\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> value </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token known-class-name class-name\">Math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">floor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token known-class-name class-name\">Math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">random</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sides</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"true\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token keyword control-flow\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> content</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'text'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> text</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">🎲 You rolled a </span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation\">value</span><span class=\"token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">!</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-highlighted=\"false\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword module\">export</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> handler </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">as</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token constant\">GET</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> handler </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">as</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token constant\">POST</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> handler </span><span class=\"token keyword module\">as</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token constant\">DELETE</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\">An example MCP server with a single tool call.</p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">The majority of MCP clients currently only support the SSE transport option. To handle state required for the SSE transport, you can integrate a Redis server through any provider in our <a href=\"https://vercel.com/marketplace/category/storage\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">marketplace</a> like Upstash and Redis Labs.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">We’ve already seen customers successfully deploying MCP servers in production. One customer has seen <a href=\"https://x.com/rauchg/status/1919413544568701138\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">over 90% savings</a> using <a href=\"https://vercel.com/fluid\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Fluid compute</a> on Vercel versus traditional serverless. Fluid enables you to have full Node.js or Python compatibility, while having a more cost effective and performant platform for AI inference and agentic workloads.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#get-started-with-mcp\" id=\"get-started-with-mcp\">Get started with MCP \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Vercel's <a href=\"https://ai-sdk.dev/cookbook/next/mcp-tools\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI SDK has built-in support</a> for connecting your Node.js or Next.js apps to MCP servers.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">We’re looking forward to future MCP servers built with the HTTP transport and starting to explore the latest developments like OAuth support.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://x.com/shadcn/status/1917597228513853603\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Other Vercel projects like shadcn/ui</a> are exploring ways to integrate MCP. If you have suggestions for MCP server use cases on Vercel, we’d love to hear your feedback in our <a href=\"https://community.vercel.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">community</a>.</p><a class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_wrapper__TDjPR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\" href=\"https://vercel.com/templates/next.js/model-context-protocol-mcp-with-next-js\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack inline-cta_content___HJjb\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--sm-stack-direction:column;--md-stack-direction:row;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--sm-stack-gap:16px;--md-stack-gap:24px;--lg-stack-gap:24px;--xl-stack-gap:24px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:4px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK inline-cta_text__5aH50\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400\"><span class=\"inline-cta_icon__foom5\">\n        <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n         <g clip-path=\"url(#clip0_872_3186)\">\n          <circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" r=\"7.25\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></circle>\n          <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8 4.5L11.5 10.625H4.5L8 4.5Z\" fill=\"var(--ds-gray-100)\"></path>\n         </g> <defs>\n          <clipPath id=\"clip0_872_3186\">\n           <rect width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"white\"></rect>\n          </clipPath>\n         </defs>\n        </svg></span><strong>MCP Server with Next.js</strong></p>\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\">Get started building your first MCP server on Vercel.</p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:flex-start;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK inline-cta_cta__uN1sr\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:500\">Deploy now</p>\n     </div>\n    </div></a>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"></p>\n  </div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 通过支持 MCP 服务器和客户端，并提供相关工具和模板，简化了 AI 模型集成流程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 通过支持 MCP 服务器和客户端，并提供相关工具和模板，简化了 AI 模型集成流程。",
  "summary": "Vercel 现在支持部署 MCP (模型上下文协议， Model Context Protocol) 服务器和客户端，通过提供的服务器模板和 `@vercel/mcp-adapter` 包简化 AI 模型集成。MCP 被视为 AI 任务的定制工具包，与传统的 REST API 不同，它可能在幕后使用多个 API 和业务逻辑。MCP 现在支持 HTTP 和 OAuth 协议。Vercel 的 AI SDK 提供了内置支持，用于将 Node.js 或 Next.js 应用程序连接到 MCP 服务器。Vercel 上的流动计算 (Fluid compute) 因其在 AI 推理工作负载中具有成本效益而备受关注。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MCP 作为一个为 AI 任务量身定制的工具包，简化了 AI 模型集成。",
      "explanation": "MCP 与传统 REST API 不同，它封装了多个 API 和业务逻辑，为 AI 提供定制工具，简化 AI 任务的构建和集成。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Vercel 的 MCP 适配器支持 SSE 和 HTTP 传输，增强了灵活性。",
      "explanation": "`@vercel/mcp-adapter` 包支持 SSE 和无状态 HTTP 传输。开发人员可以根据客户端需求选择合适的传输方法，从而提高 MCP 服务器的灵活性和兼容性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Vercel 的 AI SDK 提供了对 MCP 服务器的内置支持。",
      "explanation": "Vercel 的 AI SDK 简化了将 Node.js 或 Next.js 应用程序连接到 MCP 服务器的过程，从而简化了 Vercel 生态系统中的 AI 集成。"
    },
    {
      "point": "流动计算显著降低了 AI 推理成本。",
      "explanation": "流动计算为 AI 推理和代理工作负载提供了一个更具成本效益的平台，与传统的 Serverless 方法相比，有望节省 90% 以上的成本。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "MCP (模型上下文协议) 是一种为 AI 模型构建集成的方式。",
    "与其将 MCP 视为 REST API，不如将其视为一个定制的工具包，可以帮助 AI 实现特定任务。",
    "流动计算使您能够拥有完整的 Node.js 或 Python 兼容性，同时拥有一个更具成本效益和高性能的 AI 推理和代理工作负载平台。"
  ],
